{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851330/extras/HOTD_SteamText1_616x83_7.png?t=1684968431\" /><br>In an age of dark fantasy, Heroes from the three great factions face off in an endless struggle for power and survival. Whose power will you embrace: the mystic Vampires, the brutal Werewolves, or the cunning Humans?<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851330/extras/HOTD_Steam_Banner1_616x345.png?t=1684968431\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851330/extras/HOTD_SteamText1_616x83_2.png?t=1684968431\" /><br>The action never stops in HotD! Day and night, your might grows as Heroes train to level up and explore dungeons to find mighty relics. You can send them on a quest now and check back later to see what weapons, armor, and treasures they\u2019ve unearthed.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851330/extras/HOTD_Steam_Banner3_616x345.png?t=1684968431\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851330/extras/HOTD_SteamText1_616x83_3.png?t=1684968431\" /><br>As you team up with other HotD players, you can challenge rival teams to 5v5 showdowns where only the most skilled and well equipped players can win! Great rewards await those who claim victory, but only one can claim the ultimate power: \u201cThe Heart of Tenebris.\u201d<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851330/extras/HOTD_Steam_Banner2_616x345.png?t=1684968431\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851330/extras/HOTD_SteamText2_616x83.png?t=1684968431\" /><br>Assembling an effective role-playing team takes more than throwing your strongest Heroes together. You must make the most of their physical, magical, and support skills, discover powerful synergies, and devise a battle plan that can unleash unspeakable devastation upon any foe!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851330/extras/HOTD_Steam_Banner5_616x345.png?t=1684968431\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851330/extras/HOTD_SteamText1_616x83_5.png?t=1684968431\" /><br>Your epic adventure begins from within a gothic mansion filled with dark magic waiting to be unlocked. As your power grows, you will unlock rooms, allowing you to unite more Heroes of darkness to your cause and granting you additional powers to bestow upon your champions.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851330/extras/HOTD_Steam_Banner4_616x345.png?t=1684968431\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851330/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1684968431","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851330/page.bg.jpg?t=1684968431","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851330/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1684968431","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851330/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1684968431","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"MMO","id":20},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Cross-Platform Multiplayer","id":27},{"description":"In-App Purchases","id":35}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851330/extras/HOTD_SteamText1_616x83_7.p